Wow as you all know I’m headed to Broadway to compete in the National Jimmy Awards #jimmyawardnominee Broadway San Diego Awards #bestactress2023 - as we just finished submitting her requirements I want to say  HUGE thank you to her support team! Auntie Caitlyn  for gifting new headshots by amazing Kathrine Rose Photography -music teachers Kara Howard and Nancy Casey for last minute coming together to record music and videos, Chelsea Robinson for her amazing editing skills of Tirzah’s essay component. To her Bestie Maya for recording  dances and interviews to be submitted! Alice and Abbi for the love, rides and support. The amazing Berg family for substantial support and encouragement ! Auntie Coty and Bruncle William  for their support as well! Can’t forget Cheryl for last minute accompaniment help. Jake Frank and Aunt Caitlyn for character analysis help. Andrew’s amazing promo reel, And I can’t leave out director Spencer Farmer and CAHS Theater for making this whole experience a possibility! And of course to All our family and friends who have for the past 14 years, as she first stepped on stage have encouraged her to pursue her dreams! NYC here she comes! #broadwaybound #tinytirzah ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️

Day 1- first plane ride ever was a success! A first view of nyc - a Jordan Fisher sighting (she is a HUGE fan)  dinner at Bond 45 for an early bday celebration with her amazing chaperone/PR guy Mark and Keegan her fellow SD winner(she is 17 tomorrow 🤩) surprise bday gifts were
Handed to her from momma and Sissy by her chaperone and she was so happy! A trip to Time square too! And she is loving the view and all the city noises!  Broadway San Diego Awards #bestactress2023 CAHS Theater goes to the The Jimmy Awards #jimmyawardnominee

Day 2 success!! And who is that that walked through the doors and on my birthday but none other than ⭐️BEN PLATT ⭐️one of
My faves!!! So happy that yes he is in tell twice!! Day was packed with dancing , singing and yep even abd workout (it’s not all fun an games being a star!) and oh a special Bday celebrating thanks to @mark.anthony.beltran  and @broadwaysdawards  as well as my pod leader Paige! ❤️🥳 THIS IS 17!!!! #bestacrress2023 #broadwaysandiego @cahstheatre goes to @jimmyawards #jimmyawardnominee #benplatt⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️

Day 4 in NYC! Day 3 Jimmy prep 12 hour rehearsal days rewarded today with a trip to Sardi’s famous restaurant and @mjthemusical  and ummm wait what’s that oh yah ME on a GIANT billboard in TimeSquare!!! Amazing  and yay got to FaceTime mom @jodiraeskish  and big sis @the.rae.rae when I was there! Wow!! 5 days til show night!!! @cahstheatre  goes to @jimmyawards  #bestactress2023 @jimmyawards #tinytirzah #broadwaybound

#repost @aemeditor thank you for this inspiring reel! I will return to Broadway and once again perform!! @cahstheatre goes to @jimmyawards #bestactress2023 @broadwaysdawards #jimmyawardnominee #tinytirzah #broadwaydebut

location.city_name: Minskoff Theatre, Broadway, NYC, New York

social_posts.post_text:
Thank you to all of you for your support I heard from hometown to Japan, besties to friends of friends and even Broadway Stars! I got as  many in who sent pics and wishes but I know I mist have missed some as several went to different accounts of mine)  @jimmyawards  was an experience I will never forget and one I am honored to have had! Emotions were high as I couldn’t wait to see and hug my family and friends!  I met @andrewbfeldman_ (former winner) and @mckenziekurtz (former nominee) and ummm @corbinbleu was the host!  I still can’t believe I sang center stage at the MINSKOFF theater!! I was on Broadway!!!! 
⭐️ @cahstheatre  goes to @jimmyawards #bestactress2023 @broadwaysdawards #tinytirzah #broadwaydebut #dreamscometrue #broadwaycasting

Finally picked up yesterday and family waited outside Juilliard and sang my song from Freaky Friday heard here - and were so excited big Sis led charge running down street to meet me and between her, mom and bestie  they didn’t leave my side! still wiped from 8 days of 12 hour rehearsals and a big
Broadway debut for sure but still have a few days of NYC fun ahead! More NYC updates to come!  @cahstheatre  goes to @jimmyawards  #bestactress2023 @broadwaysdawards #tinytirzah #broadwaydebut

So busy touring #nyc my reels are behind but fun times we’re had at the  Broadway Museum! #annie memories , Hair, West side and so so much more! And of course I am in the 2023 slot for what’s on Broadway!! #Broadwaydebut @jimmyawards - the Museum was a great start to my time with my family!

#bestactress2023 @broadwaysdawards  #tinytirzah #broadwaydebut  #nyc #triplethreat #jimmyawardnominee

First night with family we were off to dinner (I was dying for some steak!!!) and @chicagomusical  mom’s great friend @rd.lowe stars in the show so we were all excited! Had great seats and got to meet of course Mary Sunshine, Velma and Mama! The dancing in this show was phenomenal and the vocals (wow!) even flat Tirzah came as she has traveled to See the show and be on stage with Ryan when O was little and created her!! @cahstheatre  goes to @jimmyawards #bestactress2023 @broadwaysdawards #tinytirzah takes #nyc #broadwaydebut

Day 2 with the family! #wicked day! Started at famous Stardust diner for breakfast then off to Disney store- I mean when you’re an avid Mickey fan you have to visit the NYC branch! Wicked was amazing and we met Fiyero @litzjordan and Glinda @mckenziekurtz and she remembered me from the Jimmy’s 😊 we about fell asleep at the bar while we waited to head to famous Sardi’s where we ran into one of our fave characters from New York, New York (pic in later reel). So thankful for having so much fun and for her Berg family Glad they came into my life!! 
- @cahstheatre goes to @jimmyawards #bestactress2023 @broadwaysdawards #tinytirzah #broadwaydebut #tinytirzahtakesnyc

@sweeneytoddbway was an amazing day started at the  Chelsea peirs to see Ellis Island and The Statue of Liberty! Off to the Harry Potter Store and omg Sweeney where I got an autograph and a thumbs up from @joshgroban )that’s some serious Broadway luck) met @annaleighashford and @gatenm123  such an amazing show!!! 
@cahstheatre @jimmyawards  #bestactress2023 @broadwaysdawards  #tinytirzahtakesnyc #tinytirzah #broadwaydebut

Tea @the plaza hotel to finally celebrate my birthday with Mom and Sis! It was AMAZING and Sis @the.rae.rae lived all her Eloise dreams 💞💖 off to Central Park made it to the fountain and just thought “Matt Bomer has been here!!” More little us fun as we enjoyed the American Girl store and of course “Annie” finally made it to Bergdorff - but no new coat too hot #ifykyk  and that’s just the first half of my Un- “birthday” celebration day! 
#tinytirzahtakesnyc #tinytirzah #broadwaydebut #bestactress2023 @broadwaysdawards #jimmyawardnominee @jimmyawards

This is NOT over yet -
for sure! More NYC fun on my un- “birthday” celebration day! Mom and I went to  @topoftherocknyc  it was amazing can’t imagine how much better when there is no smoke in air! Also did a tour of the Rockefeller  Center- Then dinner where my waiter treated me with a huge mocktail AND giant brownie sundae!! The topper of the day was @bensplatt  in @paradebway  the entire cast and show was beyond amazing!! Absolutely loved  @jake.ped  as Frankie and was great to see him and Ben Platt after their speaking @jimmyawards  a few days prior! A huge highlight was catching @alexjgsings after and chatting he was so encouraging and man what talent!! GO SEE THIS SHOW but hurry it closes in August! One last walk through Times Square and well memories of my brownie because it was the best I’ve ever had! 
#bestactress2023 @broadwaysdawards  #tinytirzahtakesnyc #tinytirzah #broadwaysdebut #itsnotoveryetnyc

Headed home July 1 after two amazing weeks in NYC! Grabbed a hot dog in Central a park before we left.  And then Surprise the next day at my favorite Pizza place a group of friends and family surprised me for a welcome back and show of support!! Thank you all who came it was amazing! This was a trip of an lifetime and I will definitely be back to #thebigapple performing on #broadway again someday! Don’t worry still some more @jimmyawards photos and Broadway star reels to come! Thanks for sharing in the adventure! @cahstheatre  goes to the @jimmyawards  #bestactress2023 @broadwaysdawards #tinytrzahtakesnyc #tinytirzah #broadwaydebut

Star struck week for sure! I spent the week @jimmyawards  in vocal coaching with @desioakley  she was amazing!! Had a session with @bensplatt - met @gatenm123 after Sweeney Todd - Josh GROBIN, Analeigh Ashford, @rd.lowe , @misskimizzo , @jkfouche , @mckenziekurtz , @litzjordan cast of @mjthemusical  and @paradebway  ran into a member of @nynybway  at @sardisnyc  and @andrewbfeldman_  so many stars in such a short time and all of them were so encouraging - if they heard I was a #jimmyawardnominee they were congratulating and so encouraging of my career!! What an inspiring week!!

@cahstheatre  goes to @jimmyawards  #bestactress2023 @broadwaysdawards #tinytirzahtakesnyc #tinytirzah #broadwaydebut

I had the Grooviest 17th birthday disco party ! “Panic at the disco groove!” Murder Mystery! Thanks so much for all that came and participated in your fun roles! So happy to finally celebrate with my friends and family! #dancingqueen #murdermystery #17thbirthday #tinytirzah

It’s been 2 1/2 weeks since @jimmyawards  and 1 1/2 weeks since I’ve returned from being in my own dreams in #thebigapple and 😢 I miss it so much! So thankful for the opportunity  from @broadwaysdawards - a dream come true a miracle just for me that my tiny self dreamt of being on a #broadway stage  and now I can say I have and begin my dream and hard work to return! I met so many great and talented new friends!! And the long 12 hour rehearsal days were tough but worth with great direction we put on an amazing show that you can now see⭐️ https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6LkzOSrb0sBAI7n-ddowk-zn8i9Tt0aY ⭐️ such great memories and I miss being amongst the city noises and buildings! #iwillreturn @cahstheatre  goes to #jimmyawards2023 #tinytirzah #broadwaydebut #broadwaybound bestactress2023 #jimmyawardnominre

#tinkerbell times @disneyland for my bestie @_mayaberg_  birthday what better way to spend an 18th bday then at the one place where we never have to grow up!! 💚thanks so much @mnmberg  for the amazing trip💚My Tink ears from @gleamandglimmerco  were perfect for the event along with my @loungefly  bag! #tinkerbellandfriends #pixiehollow #peterpan #disneybound #tinytirzah #teenmodel #teeninfluencer#disneyinfluencer  #industrykid #actor #broadwaybound
